The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-03-2013 FRI...........PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program


The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET

        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 1/3/14Friday, January 03, 2014 11:45 AM




Doc and Skip are in for Glenn and they're shedding some light on a funny fact.

  All the major media outlets are reporting that the crew of the ship stuck in the arctic ice
       has been rescued,
         but no one is reporting what they were doing there..
              .studying global warming! 

 So the crew studying global WARMING got stuck in FREEZING ICE.

  Also, a comedian makes a rash comment about WW2 vets and the guys are pissed.

  Plus, the federal government is getting involved in what you eat.
  Now it's vending machines,

       Doc and Skip explain.
